            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/md/aktuelt/nyheter/2010/Environmental-technology----lessons-learned-in-Romania-and-Norway.html?id=615277" title="">
                        Environmental technology  - lessons learned in Romania and Norway
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[News story, Ministry of the Environment, 23.09.2010]</p>
                <p>The Romanian Ministry of Environment and Forests and the Norwegian Ministry of Environment cooperate to promote environmental technology and green public procurement. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
