            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/press/news/2010/fight_aids.html?id=614806" title="">
                        Norway to donate NOK 1.4 billion to the Global Fund to Fight AIDS, Tuberculosis and Malaria 
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 22.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Norway is to increase its contribution to the Global Fund to Fight AIDS, Tuberculosis and Malaria by NOK 75 million, making the total Norwegian contribution NOK 450 million per year. This is equivalent to an increase of 20%, and it means that Norway will donate almost NOK 1.4 billion to the Fund over the next three years.   </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp2098008319_wp1868745181_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl01_Label1"></span>                 
