        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/aktuelt/taler_artikler/utenriksministeren/2010/breakfast_remarks.html?id=615731" title="">
                        Remarks at Ministerial Breakfast on Health and Foreign Policy
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">New York, 22 September 2010 </h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 22.09.2010]</p>
                <p>"So, what have we accomplished? One of our main goals was to give global health a more strategic place on the international agenda. And this is indeed happening. The G8 summit in June gave a big boost to work on child and maternal mortality”, Foreign Minister Støre said in his remarks.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp2098008319_wp1868745181_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl02_Label1"></span>                 
